        <h2>How Social Media Affects Our Studies</h2>
        <p>Social media has become a significant part of our daily lives, but for students, especially those preparing for <span class="highlight">MDCAT</span>, it can be a major distraction.</p>
        
        <p>Constant notifications and the habit of endless scrolling reduce our "Deep Work" capability. To succeed, we must learn to manage our screen time effectively.</p>
